<div class="page-title title-with-sep single-title">
<h1 class="entry-title">A luxurious and futuristic private jet cabin by Lufthansa and Mercedes-Benz</h1>
</div>
<span class="entry-author">
<span class="written-by">by</span>
<span class="author vcard">
<a class="url fn n" href="https://luxurylaunches.com/author/shayne/" rel="author" data-wpel-link="internal">Shayne Rana</a>
</span>
</span>
</header>
